caption:
It's still October, and it's still Breast Cancer Awareness month.

Board-certified OB-GYN @therealdrjackie - and cast member of @bravotv Married to Medicine - is a two-time breast cancer survivor who has turned her personal pain into a passion for nurturing the emotional & physical needs of women (and men) diagnosed with breast cancer via her 50 Shades of Pink Foundation, an organization established in 2013 to treat the inner & outer beauty of cancer survivors.

During October, we're donating 20% of the proceeds of the sales of Dr. Jackie's two Skin Rhythm products to 50 Shades of Pink.

Whether you buy these products from @ultabeauty @dermstore or volitionbeauty.com the proceeds will all go to Dr. Jackie's foundation this month.

#breastcancer #breastcancerawareness #breastcancerawarenessmonth #50shadesfpink #obgyn #hormonalacne #hormonalskin
